        <Meaning id="a96194d4-0c6e-41f5-be9b-59bda7ae9608" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Tinh trùng</Vi>
          <En>The male reproductive cell, which fertilizes the female egg to initiate development of a new organism.</En>
          <Example>Each ejaculation contains hundreds of millions of sperm cells.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="7e217d76-dc95-4be2-a8dc-b34bea649e9c">
